---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for No Lock-In Printer, including analytics, email signup, affiliate links, and third-party services."
>
  <article class="article">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--amber);">Privacy policy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">This policy explains what No Lock-In Printer may collect and how the site uses common third-party services.</p>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        The current site is a static website. We do not require accounts. If an email signup or contact form is enabled, we may collect the information you choose to submit, such as your email address and message.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Analytics and hosting</h2>
      <p>
        The site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may process request metadata such as IP address, user agent, URL, and security signals to deliver and protect the site. Analytics providers may process page views, referral data, browser details, or similar technical information to help us understand site usage.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Advertising cookies</h2>
      <p>No Lock-In Printer may use third-party advertising services, including Google AdSense. Third-party vendors, including Google, may use cookies, web beacons, IP addresses, or similar identifiers to serve and measure ads based on a visitor's prior visits to this website or other websites.</p>
      <p>You can control or opt out of personalized Google advertising through <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/">Google Ads Settings</a>. Additional industry opt-out choices are available at <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/">aboutads.info</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
      <p>
        Outbound retailer links may include affiliate or sponsored tracking parameters. Those third-party sites have their own privacy policies and may collect information after you leave No Lock-In Printer.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Privacy questions can be sent to <a href="mailto:hello@nolockinprinter.com">hello@nolockinprinter.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
    <p>Last updated July 11, 2026.</p>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
